          "source_code": "def reverse_string(input_string) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"反转输入字符串并返回包含反转后字符串的字典。\n\n    参数:\n        input_string (str): 要反转的字符串。\n\n    返回:\n        dict: 包含 'reversed_string' 键的字典，如果输入无效则包含 'error' 键。\n    \"\"\"\n    if not isinstance(input_string, str):\n        return {'error': 'input_string must be a string'}\n    reversed_str = input_string[::-1]\n    return {'reversed_string': reversed_str}",
